// Copy this file to `Local.xcconfig` (which is git-ignored) and set your Apple
// Development Team ID below.
//
// Find your Team ID in Xcode → Settings → Accounts (select your team), or run:
//   security find-certificate -c "Apple Development" -p | openssl x509 -noout -subject
// and use the 10-character code in the OU= field.
//
// Leaving it blank still builds, but Xcode will ask you to pick a team the
// first time you Run, and macOS may re-prompt for permissions across rebuilds.

DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOUR_TEAM_ID
